-- Israel’s Liberman Says Iran Racing to Bomb, Ynet Reports
-- B y   A m y   T e i b e l
-- 2013-05-28T07:22:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-28/israel-s-liberman-says-iran-racing-to-bomb-ynet-reports.html
Chairman of parliament’s foreign
affairs and defense committee, Avigdor Liberman, tells panel
 Iran  speeding toward bomb at “insane pace,’ Ynet news website
says today.
* Says he hopes Israel ‘‘will know how to make the right
decisions’’
* NOTE: Iran says its nuclear energy program is designed for
energy production and medical use
